CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 13, 1971, pg. 33, reads: "Accepts Keys... Mrs. Hilliard Jordan, Jr., along with first place winner of the Courier Baby Contest Hilliard Jordan III, accepts keys to a 1972 Dodge Dart Swinger from Bob Hunzinger, Sales Manager Burgunder Dodge of Bridgeville, Rod Doss, Acting Advertising Director of the Courier, looks on at left. The car, along with 1,000 gallons of gasoline, was awarded as First Prize in Courier's Annual Baby Contest. (Harris Photo.)
TitMainTitle: Bob Hunzinger presenting keys to 1972 Dodge Dart Swinger to Mrs. Jordan holding Pittsburgh Courier Baby Contest winner Hilliard Jordan III, with Rod Doss looking on, at Burgunder Dodge, Bridgeville
